track_notes: Short hike on the AT and the spur trail heading to the Whitly Gap shelter.  Plenty of parking available at Hogpen Gap.

1.3 mile hike with 660 feet of EG, almost all of that in the first 0.6 miles.  Parking for 10-12 cars at Tesnatee Gap (34.726199, -83.847674).  Head northbound on the AT for 0.65 miles, then take a right on the blue-blazed side trail for the Whitly AT Shelter to Wildcat Mtn.
track_title: W4G/NG-020 - Wildcat Mtn via Tesnatee Gap
